munities<ref name=\"petermackay-myplan\"/>\n|\n*\n|\n*Meet the 2% of GDP targets for defence spending set out by [[NATO]] within five years<ref>{{cite web |title=A Strong Canada Through A Strong Defense (sic) |url=https://www.dereksloan.ca/strong_defense |website=Derek Sloan for Leader|access-date = 19 April 2020}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|Foreign\n|\n*Withdraw from the UN [[Global Compact for Migration]]<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n*Move Canada's embassy in [[Israel]] to Jerusalem<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n*Redirect money from foreign aid to providing Indigenous reserves with clean drinking water<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n*Remove abortion funding from foreign aid<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n|\n*Prevent [[Huawei]] from entering Canada's 5G Networks<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://petermackay.ca/en-CA/huawei|title=No Huawei in 5G Networks &#124; Peter MacKay|website=petermackay.ca}}</ref>\n*Increase regulation of Foreign state-owned companies investments in Canada's critical infrastructure<ref name=\"petermackay-myplan\"/>\n*Withdraw from international conventions that conflict with Canadian law, basic human rights, and Canada\u2019s national interest<ref name=\"petermackay-myplan\"/>\n|\n*Support creating a [[CANZUK]] agreement on trade<ref>{{cite web |title=CANZUK Deal |url=https://erinotoole.ca/canzuk/ |website=Erin O'Toole |access-date=7 April 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504033025/http://erinotoole.ca/canzuk/ |archive-date=4 May 2019 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|\n*Remove abortion funding from foreign aid<ref name=\"life\">{{cite web |title=Respect For Human Life |url=https://www.dereksloan.ca/respect_for_human_life |website=Derek Sloan for Leader|access-date = 19 April 2020}}</ref>\n*Oppose  [[UNDRIP]]<ref name=\"Soverienty\">{{cite web |title=Canadian Soverienty |url=https://www.dereksloan.ca/canadian_sovereignty |website=Derek Sloan for Leader|access-date = 19 April 2020}}</ref>\n*Withdraw from the [[Paris Agreement]]<ref name=\"Soverienty\"/>\n*Withdraw from t